# Median of Two Sorted Arrays

## Descriptions

[original description](https://leetcode.com/problems/median-of-two-sorted-arrays/)

## Solutions

### First Idea

```javascript
/**
 * @param {number[]} nums1
 * @param {number[]} nums2
 * @return {number}
 */
var findMedianSortedArrays = function (nums1, nums2) {
  const len = nums1.length + nums2.length;
  const max = len % 2 ? (len - 1) / 2 : len / 2;
  let prev = null;
  let pprev = null;

  let cur1 = 0;
  let cur2 = 0;

  for (let i = 0; i <= max; i++) {
    pprev = prev;
    prev =
      (nums1[cur1] ?? Number.MAX_VALUE) < (nums2[cur2] ?? Number.MAX_VALUE)
        ? nums1[cur1++]
        : nums2[cur2++];
  }

  return len % 2 ? prev : (pprev + prev) / 2;
};
```

- Time Complexity: O(n)
- Space Complexity: O(1)
